          "Write a sentence using the term analytically, not descriptively."
        ]
      },
      open: {
        main: "The precise critical vocabulary we bring to Ono's nostalgia — whether we call it 'nostalgia,' 'denial,' or 'revisionism' — fundamentally shapes the argument we make. How does your choice of term position you as a reader?",
