        main: "What specific historical and literary vocabulary should an analyst use when discussing propaganda art and artistic complicity in pre-war Japan — and how do these terms enrich a reading of Ono?",
        steps: [
          "Define 'complicity', 'propaganda' and 'revisionism' as they apply to wartime art.",
          "Apply one term to Ono's implied past as a propaganda artist.",
